"most are able to receive a full multiplex, so you usually only need one per "
"频率/复用器. You can quickly 检查 if your 调谐器 supports \"full 复用器 receive\" by "
"going to the _Muxes_ 标签页 and playing a freq/复用器 in something like VLC."

