"only once detailed actual-TS data has actually been received. Inspired by "
"VDR's adaptive EIT handling."
msgstr ""
"The Adaptive policy is self-correcting per 服务: it suppresses other-TS only "
"once detailed actual-TS 数据 has actually been received. Inspired by VDR's "
"adaptive EIT handling."

#: src/docs_inc.c:280
msgid ""
"The EPG tab displays a filterable grid containing all events, sorted based "
"on start time."
msgstr ""
"The EPG 标签页 displays a filterable 网格 containing all 事件, sorted based on 开始 "
"时间."

#: src/docs_inc.c:4439
msgid ""
"The HTSP profile, generally used with HTSP clients such as Kodi and Movian."
msgstr ""
"The HTSP 配置方案, generally used with HTSP clients such as Kodi and Movian."

#: src/docs_inc.c:3904
msgid ""
"The OTA broadcast data often does not have specific dedicated fields to "
"describe the programme season, episode, etc. Sometimes this information is "
"included in the programme summary."
msgstr ""
"The OTA 广播 数据 often does not have specific dedicated 字段 to describe the 节目 "
"季, 剧集, etc. Sometimes this 信息 is included in the 节目 摘要."

#: src/docs_inc.c:1094
msgid ""
"The Tvheadend software then sets up a series of configuration elements, and "
"the way in which these interact determines how a TV signal ends up in front "
"of you. They all use what's known as a _many-to-many_ relationship, in that "
"one configuration element can be related to multiple elements of the next "
"type, and vice versa: one tuner has multiple networks, one network can exist"
" on multiple tuners."
msgstr ""
"The Tvheadend 软件 then sets up a 系列 of 配置 elements, and the way in which "
"these interact determines how a 电视 信号 ends up in front of you. They all use "
"what's known as a _many-to-many_ relationship, in that one 配置 element can be"
" related to multiple elements of the 下一个 类型, and vice versa: one 调谐器 has "
"multiple 网络, one 网络 can exist on multiple 调谐器."

#: src/docs_inc.c:1500
msgid ""
"The _Auto refresh_ check-box allows the interface to automatically refresh "
"the rows for you, every 30 seconds."
msgstr ""
"The _Auto refresh_ 检查-box allows the 界面 to automatically refresh the rows "
"for you, every 30 seconds."

#: src/docs_inc.c:2730
msgid ""
"The _Auto-recording (Autorecs)_ tab offers many powerful features, regular "
"expressions for title, synopsis and description event matching, duplicate "
"episode handling, time-frame based rules and much more!"
msgstr ""
"The _Auto-录像 (Autorecs)_ 标签页 offers many powerful features, regular "
"expressions for 标题, synopsis and 描述 事件 matching, duplicate 剧集 handling, 时间-"
"frame based 规则 and much more!"

#: src/docs_inc.c:4895
msgid ""
"The _Change parameters_ flag allows you to control which parameters "
"(permission flags, all types of profiles, channel tags and ranges) are "
"combined when multiple entries match a username/login. When the change "
"parameter flag is enabled (checked) for a parameter, the setting for this "
"user overrides any previous entry (though it can in turn be overridden by a "
"later entry). The exception is the __rights__ option where the permissions "
"for all matching users having the change parameter flag set are added "
"together."
msgstr ""
"The _Change parameters_ 标志 allows you to control which parameters (权限 flags,"
" all 类型 of 配置方案, 频道 标签 and ranges) are combined when multiple 条目 match a "
"username/登录. When the 更改 parameter 标志 is 已启用 (checked) for a parameter, the "
"设置 for this 用户 overrides any 上一个 条目 (though it can in turn be overridden by "
"a later 条目). The exception is the __rights__ 选项 where the permissions for "
"all matching 用户 having the 更改 parameter 标志 set are added together."

