#: src/docs_inc.c:1096
msgid ""
"The __network__ is the software definition of your carrier network. Broadly,"
" it lays out what sort of network it is (such as DVB-T or DVB-S2), how it "
"gets scanned, where the DVB-S satellite is in orbit, and similar. Networks "
"are used by tuners so the hardware knows where to look for a signal."
msgstr ""
"The __network__ is the 软件 definition of your carrier 网络. Broadly, it lays "
"out what sort of 网络 it is (such as DVB-T or DVB-S2), how it gets scanned, "
"where the DVB-S 卫星 is in orbit, and similar. 网络 are used by 调谐器 so the 硬件 "
"knows where to look for a 信号."

#: src/docs_inc.c:5757
msgid ""
"The `$B` and `$A` formats also have numeric modifiers to specify when zero "
"padded values are required."
msgstr ""
"The `$B` and `$A` formats also have numeric modifiers to specify when zero "
"padded 值 are 必需."

#: src/docs_inc.c:5733
msgid ""
"The `$Q` and `$q` formats also have two numeric modifiers to select variant "
"formats and can be used as `$1Q`, `$2Q`, `3Q`, `$1q`, `$2q`, and `$3q`."
msgstr ""
"The `$Q` and `$q` formats also have two numeric modifiers to 选择 variant "
"formats and can be used as `$1Q`, `$2Q`, `3Q`, `$1q`, `$2q`, and `$3q`."

