"to the specific MPEG-TS PIDs."
msgstr "快速扫描频道包在配置树中预定义。必须手动启用这些频道包，Tvheadend 才能订阅并监听特定的 MPEG-TS PID。"

#: src/docs_inc.c:314
msgid ""
"The filter uses case-insensitive regular expressions. If you don’t know what"
" a regular expression is, this simply means that you can type just parts of "
"the title and filter on that - there’s no need for full, exact matching. If "
"the fulltext checkbox is checked, the title text is matched against title, "
"subtitle, summary and description. If the mergetext checkbox is checked, the"
" title text is matched against a merger of the title + subtitle + summary + "
"description + credits + keywords. See AutoRec help for more details on using"
" mergetext."
msgstr ""
"The 过滤 uses case-insensitive regular expressions. If you don’t know what a "
"regular expression is, this simply means that you can 类型 just parts of the "
"标题 and 过滤 on that - there’s no need for full, exact matching. If the "
"fulltext checkbox is checked, the 标题 文本 is matched against 标题, 副标题, 摘要 and "
"描述. If the mergetext checkbox is checked, the 标题 文本 is matched against a "
"merger of the 标题 + 副标题 + 摘要 + 描述 + credits + keywords. See 自动录制 帮助 for more "
"详情 on using mergetext."

#: src/docs_inc.c:666
msgid ""
"The first part of the wizard is where you select the basic language "
"settings, if you don't enter a preferred language, US English will be used "
"as a default. Not selecting the correct EPG language can result in garbled "
"EPG text; if this happens, don't panic, as you can easily change it later."
msgstr ""
"The 第一个 part of the 向导 is where you 选择 the basic language 设置, if you don't "
"enter a preferred language, US English will be used as a 默认. Not selecting "
"the correct EPG language can result in garbled EPG 文本; if this happens, "
"don't panic, as you can easily 更改 it later."

#: src/docs_inc.c:6427
msgid ""
"The first part of this covers the network details for address-based access "
"to the system; for example, 192.168.1.0/24 to allow local access only to "
"192.168.1.x clients, or 0.0.0.0/0 or empty value for access from any system."
msgstr ""
"The 第一个 part of this covers the 网络 详情 for 地址-based 访问 to the 系统; for "
"example, 192.168.1.0/24 to 允许 local 访问 only to 192.168.1.x clients, or "
"0.0.0.0/0 or empty 值 for 访问 from any 系统."

#: src/docs_inc.c:678
