"The 第一个 part of this covers the 网络 详情 for 地址-based 访问 to the 系统; for "
"example, 192.168.1.0/24 to 允许 local 访问 only to 192.168.1.x clients, or "
"0.0.0.0/0 or empty 值 for 访问 from any 系统. This works alongside the second "
"part, which is a familiar username/密码 combination, so provide these for both"
" an administrator and regular (day-to-day) 用户."

